# Потоки

## Клиент (`/api/*`, guard `client`)

| # | Действие | BC | POL / ADR |
|---|----------|-----|-----------|
| 1 | Bootstrap (контент, прайс) | PublicSite → Company + Pricing | ADR-004 |
| 2 | SubmitSiteLead + intake_data | ClientPortal | ≠ Order |
| 3 | Register / profile / password | ClientPortal | — |
| 4 | Заказы active / history | ClientPortal → Order (read) | ADR-005: без статусов цеха |
| 5 | SubmitReview | ClientPortal → Order | POL-04: только issued |

## Мастер (`/api/pos/*`, Sanctum, master_id = self)

| # | Действие | BC | POL |
|---|----------|-----|-----|
| 1 | Login | Identity | — |
| 2 | TakeOrderToWork | OrderFulfillment | POL-06; после AssignMaster (ADR-006) |
| 3 | waiting_parts / resume / works / notes | OrderFulfillment | — |
| 4 | MarkOrderReady | OrderFulfillment | POL-01 |
| 5 | Search equipment / warehouse | Equipment, Warehouse | read-only |
| — | completed tab | — | = ready, не issued |
| — | rework_feedback | OrderFulfillment (read) | после ReturnOrderForRework |

**Не в POS:** CreateOrder, AssignMaster, цены, материалы, Issue, Cancel, rework, PDF.

## Менеджер (Filament `/cp`)

| # | Действие | BC | POL |
|---|----------|-----|-----|
| 1 | Lead → CreateOrder | ClientPortal → OrderFulfillment + Company | POL-09; LeadToOrderFormData |
| 2 | AssignMasterToOrder | OrderFulfillment | POL-08 |
| 3 | SetWorkPrices + RecalculateOrderPrice | OrderFulfillment | POL-05 |
| 4 | AddMaterial / LinkEquipment | OrderFulfillment → Warehouse, Equipment | read warehouse |
| 5 | ReturnOrderForRework | OrderFulfillment | POL-11/12; Filament only (ADR-008) |
| 6 | IssueOrder + PDF | OrderFulfillment → read models | POL-02; ADR-003 |
| 7 | CancelOrder | OrderFulfillment | POL-03: только new |
| 8 | LinkGuestOrders, модерация Review | ClientPortal → Order | — |
| — | CRUD справочников | Company, Pricing, Warehouse, Equipment, Identity | вне основного потока |

## Сквозной happy path

```
SubmitSiteLead → [менеджер] CreateOrder + AssignMaster
→ [мастер] TakeOrderToWork → works → MarkOrderReady
→ [менеджер] SetWorkPrices + Recalculate → IssueOrder
→ [клиент] SubmitReview
```

## Cross-BC orchestration

| Сценарий | Handler / Builder | Порты |
|----------|-------------------|-------|
| Lead → Order | CreateOrderHandler | SiteLead, Branch |
| Bootstrap | GetPublicBootstrapQueryHandler | Company, Pricing |
| ЛК заказы | GetClientOrders*, GetClientOrderDetail* | Order |
| Отзыв | SubmitReviewHandler | Order |
| Гость → Client | LinkGuestOrdersToClientHandler | Order |
| Материал | AddMaterialToOrderHandler | WarehouseItem |
| Оборудование | LinkEquipmentToOrderHandler | Equipment |
| PDF | GenerateDocumentHandler + OrderDocumentReadModelBuilder | Company, Identity, Equipment, Warehouse |
| POS карточка | PosOrderReadModelBuilder | Equipment, Master, WarehouseItem |
| История ремонта | GetEquipmentOrderHistoryQueryHandler | Order |

Правило: cross-BC только в Application Handler или ReadModel Builder; Domain — только `*_id`.
